Arm Developer
 +4
Performance Engineering & Profiling
GPU Performance Engineering (NHR@FAU): An advanced course using NVIDIA Nsight Systems and Nsight Compute to identify application bottlenecks through resource-based models.
AI Systems Performance Engineering (O'Reilly): Focuses on the Roofline Model to determine if workloads are compute-bound or memory-bound.
Deep Learning Performance (NVIDIA Docs): Official documentation and tutorials on optimizing Tensor Cores, mixed-precision training, and CUDA Graphs. 
