Vendor-Specific Platforms
AMD ROCm Training Videos: Tutorials on the HIP programming language, Omniperf for roofline analysis, and porting CUDA code to AMD GPUs.
CUDA Programming Course (YouTube): A practical guide to setting up the CUDA Toolkit and writing high-performance C++ kernels.
AI Infrastructure Learning Track (GitHub): A community-driven curriculum covering inter-GPU communication (NCCL) and tensor parallelism. 
